title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: Before extraction, the labels returned from getcolumnlabel are null. After extraction, the labels are recognizable strings.
EB: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings. The labels returned from getcolumnlabel before extraction should be the same as the labels returned after extraction, since they need to be displayed to the end user.
